channel.title: Ricky Wilson's Art Jam
channel.desc: Award-winning pop star Nadine Coyle visits the Art Jam studio to show Ricky three items that mean the world to her - her make-up palette, a lucky ring from India and a very special family picture. While chatting to Ricky, Nadine shares amazing stories about being in one of the biggest girl bands of all time Girls Aloud, her incredible sleeping ability, having a big family and enjoying cooking with her daughter.
